{"tid":1855282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新方向 增加口罩再用率","createTime":"2020-02-01T04:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T04:11:41.000Z","uid":30791,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"617d6232bf57a3c19d6f8712bf3a598b8ffa3ad2","tid":1855282,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"一般建議係每 4-8 小時換一次<br />\n但係如果係口罩外再加上一層保護 或者可以減少口罩外層被污染既機率<br />\n繼而增加重用口罩既安全性<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>出現口罩荒之時，K Kwong就建議出外時用太陽帽遮面，亦可在口罩外加圍巾。圍巾可阻隔外來灰塵，保持口罩外層乾淨，令口罩能用足一天，而圍巾要每天清潔。除了外科口罩，其實市面上的活性碳口罩、防花粉海綿口罩等仍有售，雖然防病毒功能不大，但K Kwong指至少可防飛沬，市民亦可考慮。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200130/NZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200130%2FNZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4%2F&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=a6bec7a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200130%2FNZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4%2F&h=83feec10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200130/NZGTQDUHYQWWOYIIZ6WPKVO6I4/</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ne.g. 戴住口罩使用:<br />\na) 面罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1R8ToD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1R8ToD.png&h=76c23a1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nb) 太陽帽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEWprOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEWprOQ.png&h=46f6edd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nc) 電單車頭盔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUwprNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUwprNC.png&h=a5978e8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a966d09699fde2b01bb3b2a653d593d242811d4d","tid":1855282,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef30d20876a95d475c16c78e725d35ac7808659","tid":1855282,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c52797d66a3665543bdbedbb3e5ba1547c4ec12","tid":1855282,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"太陽帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有用不過笑住先"},{"pid":"b2926132a8b2b5da1e0a19160b52aad034613b74","tid":1855282,"uid":55917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"4-8 係因為你"},{"pid":"4d0db602fddecd9adc2957cd7398d93fdc9b8221","tid":1855282,"uid":77277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"唔戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n直接用大頭佛電單車頭盔得唔得"},{"pid":"ca5a7bad00abea74bf6c968aa9db82e6eafcca1b","tid":1855282,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"唔係ON9啦4-8小時換, 好多貨咩<br />\n1日用1個頂住先啦"},{"pid":"964fe48c8ab8738420db6755e709bd29bdea315d","tid":1855282,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d0db602fddecd9adc2957cd7398d93fdc9b8221","tid":1855282,"uid":77277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"唔戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n直接用大頭佛電單車頭盔得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:06:05.000Z","msg":"我認為唔係得唔得既問題<br />\n因為口罩本身都唔係 100% 安全<br />\n<br />\n個問題係點樣減少傳染既機會<br />\n咁戴頭盔的確係比唔戴可以減少被傳染機會<br />\n係效果可能無戴口罩咁好<br />\n我覺得關鍵在於 入氣既窿夠唔夠細? 有無 filter? filter 係唔係即棄?<br />\n<br />\n不過無晒口罩 都要做其它保護措施<br />\n而如果疫情持續落去 無晒口罩似乎係必然會發生既事"},{"pid":"7f6d754305cde84e5eeabc8d48dee1e558ab2b32","tid":1855282,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"e9f05fdfcde0b673097a03ae74d0114d11f7937a","tid":1855282,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d0db602fddecd9adc2957cd7398d93fdc9b8221","tid":1855282,"uid":77277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"唔戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n直接用大頭佛電單車頭盔得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:11:41.000Z","msg":"如果口罩 同 頭盔比<br />\n頭盔擋到眼 口罩無擋到<br />\n即係頭盔減少飛沬直接掂到眼既機會<br />\n但係可能會經過氣孔吸入到飛沬<br />\n另一方面 口罩亦都唔係 100% 貼面"}]}